Package model.enemy

Class BossEnemy

java.lang.Object
model.GameObject
model.DynamicObject
model.enemy.Enemy
model.enemy.BossEnemy
All Implemented Interfaces:
Subject
public class BossEnemy extends Enemy
One type of enemy. Boss won't become bubble when collide with hero projectile, it will
decrease 0.1 of the boss life. Boss enemy can shoot the enemy projectile and the boss projectile.
